attributes.title: Let me tell you a story about this “app”
attributes.review: This “app” is not actually just an app ladies and gents, this here “app” is an undercover, mind control device. It changes you, your whole family, and even y’all’s pets. Let me tell y’all, this will hit different, I promise on my mammas amazing cornbread and gravy. So let me tell y’all about these crazy dogs first, they went from pets to pests REAL QUICK. First one comes up, boy says “give me a comb over”, I’m like huh? Boy if you don’t get outside and out of my face with this “comb over”, boy I’ve never heard of something so dumb, go bald or grab a wig. We don’t do those comb overs round here. Next one comes up and says “give me wet food, you know, from the can” I said why boy, you got dry food right there. The petty dog goes “come on you know I’m too classy for that, I want it juicy”. AND THEN BOOM, the door slams open and my wife is in the doorway BUTT NAKED with our expensive butter. She goes, “babe rub this fancy butter on me I’m about to go tan”, bih what? I said awwww screw it I get to play with it as I rub it you know? So bam almost the whole stick, and now I’m getting ready to butter up the toast with my last little bit and she turns, bends over, and says “don’t forget my butt hole”. I will not lie to you boys and girls, I lost control and put the butter on my own toast because the app finally got to me, I lost my respect for my woman and I said I want your butt hole to burn, so hell no I’m using it on MY toast. I already done got to rub you up and down, I don’t wanna touch the smelly thing anyway. And uh yeah, that’s why you shouldn’t get this app. Thanks for the visit see ya next time fellas!
